"Prevention"
]
},
"children":[
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"d15442",
"children":[
"Use of IV catheters should be reserved for patients with a proven need, and the catheter should be removed as soon as clinically possible."
]
},
{
"type":"inline-wrap",
"wrapId":"1",
"contentIds":[
"mk19_bb_id_s34_inline_t1"
],
"forceOpen":true
}
]
},
{
"type":"section",
